rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0002
rows.name:
I've got preparations to make, but
I should let Gramps know
what's happening first.

rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0003
rows.name:
If I just took off on a some random
ship without telling him, I'm sure he'd
give me hell later when I came back!

rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0004
rows.name:
I should head down the stairs
and make my way back to
Goldmund Return Port.
